Dialogs.Dialog: Let me ask you something... You turned off without saving, right？ Why？
Hey, Didn't you turn it off without saving？ Hah...
Hey... you turned it off without saving, right？ Geez...
Tell me... you turned off without saving, right？ Do you want to piss me off？
You powered off again without saving！ Why？ I'm really disappointed...
There you go again... powering off without saving. That kind of thing, Rinko definitely doesn't like...
Again, you powered off without saving. Why do you want to be hated...？ I can't forgive you anymore.
Geez... How many times have I told you not to power off without saving？ I won't allow it anymore, so brace yourself.
You know Rinko hates it when people power off without saving, right？ Not anymore.
Why don't you say "I won't do it anymore. Please forgive me"？ Then I'll forgive you. (Moushimasen, yurushite kudasai)
You must clearly say, "I won't do it again, please forgive me." Otherwise, Rinko's anger will never subside. (Moushimasen, yurushite kudasai)
Look at Rinko in the eye and say, "I won't do it again, please forgive me." Then I'll forgive you, okay？ (Moushimasen, yurushite kudasai)
Can't you just say, "I won't do it again. Please forgive me"？ It's easy. (Moushimasen, yurushite kudasai)
"I won't do it again. Please forgive me", right？ It's easy. Come on, say it. (Moushimasen, yurushite kudasai)
Didn't you hear me？ I want you to say, "I won't do it again, please forgive me." (Moushimasen, yurushite kudasai)
I didn't hear you... Start again.
What？ That was a joke, wasn't it？ One more time.
That's not going to get the message across. One more time, please.
What's that... that's not fair. Well... I'll allow it.
What was that？ Geez... I get it. I forgive you.
No way... If you say that to me, I have no choice but to forgive you... Idiot.
Did you really just say that？ Okay, I forgive you.
You can say it properly. Cherish that feeling.
Yes, of course I forgive you. Hehe.
But never do it again, okay？ Promise me.
Don't get carried away because I've forgiven you. I'm still hurt by this.
Please, don't do it again, okay？ Promise Rinko.
Are you ignoring me？ I don't like this...
Does that mean I don't have to forgive you？
"Don't power off without saving." Don't you ever learn？
That's enough！ "Don't power off without saving." Hah.
If there's something about turning off without saving, just say it clearly... It makes me sad.
What should I do...？ I know, say "I love Rinko the best." (Rinko ga ichiban daisuki.)
If you want forgiveness, say with sincerity, "I love Rinko the best"！ (Rinko ga ichiban daisuki.)
If you want forgiveness, say, "I love Rinko the best." You'll say it, won't you？ (Rinko ga ichiban daisuki.)
Hey... are you not going to say it？
You're not going to keep silent, are you...？
What？ What did you say？ I can't hear you...
I can't believe you fooled me like that...
Do you really think that kind of move is going to work on Rinko？
Yes... it's fine, I heard you right.
You're not lying, are you？ Rinko believes in you, you know？
Next... "I love you" three times. You can say it, right？ (Sukidayo.)
...Still no good. Next, say "I love you" three times！ (Sukidayo.)
I you want me to believe in you, say "I love you" three times, okay？ (Sukidayo.)
It would be nice... if you say it to me.
Geez, why are you saying that？
That's not what I mean... Get it？
Yes... that's what I wanted to hear.
I'm glad you said it to me. Rinko feels the same.
Make a promise this time. You will not erase our memories. Understand？
Are you really sorry？ Even Rinko really doesn't want to do this, so please stop it.
Don't you want to make up？ Please don't do it again. I want to cherish all the time we spend together.
Are you really going to act like that...？
Did you really reflect on it？ As punishment, say lots of words of love to Rinko.
The word for love is "aishiteru", right？
I know... then, try saying "small kick." Don't think too much about the meaning. (ko kikku.)
Look, my stomach is making noises.
Okay！ I received your words of love...
Not bad. You set a new record！
I don't feel like you're feeling sorry. In a case like this, you should write an apology letter.
Okay, I'll admit that you are feeling very sorry.
Hmm！ A new record has been set.
Are you really sorry for what you did？ If so, look at Rinko in the eye. If you look away or move, you're out.
That's it. Now you only have to look at Rinko.
Hehe... you always look at Rinko this seriously.
New record！ I can still stare at you, right？
I'll give up this time... For real, reflect on this.
I can't help it... I'll give you a break this time.
